{"about_the_game":"<br><br>Welcome to the first game by Under The Sink - KryptaFM! We're very honored to greet you all in front of your devices. We'll begin with a message after which you'll be met with plenty of useful tips, in case you'd like to start your adventure.<br><br>We're going to move to Gozdary, a small village in Poland. The residents have noticed a lot of weird, paranormal things going on. The areas have been haunted by an alleged cryptid from Gozdary, who leaves tracks that are leading us to solving this puzzle. Listen to the broadcasts - valuable intel might be hidden within the messages!<br><br>We'd love to invite you on our studio's social media platforms where you can share your experiences with KryptaFM! <strong>Happy hunting!</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay contains:</h2><br><strong>Nostalgic climate of a Polish village from early 2000s</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2973390/extras/zwiedzaniewsi.gif?t=1721408420\" /><br><br><strong>Nod to early-internet webforum era</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2973390/extras/przegladanieforum.gif?t=1721408420\" /><br><br><strong>Full voiceacting of radio broadcasts!</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2973390/extras/audycjanapisy.gif?t=1721408420\" /><br><br><strong>...and much more to discover!</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A close encounter of the Mietek kind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2973390/e4830ce025904a5ffef7ddaa23364f8e4bbab747.jpg"},{"name":"Full-time cryptozoologist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2973390/79abacd3a2fa30ea367a04f7560b5315bd84164e.jpg"},{"name":"You'll ruin your eyes!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps